===Etymology===
From {{etyl|af}} {{term|aardvarken}} (obsolete), {{term|erdvark}}, from {{etyl|af}} {{term|aarde||earth|lang=af}}, (from {{etyl|nl}}, from {{etyl|dum}} {{term|aerde|lang=dum}}) + {{etyl|af}} {{term|vark||pig|lang=af}}, (from {{etyl|dum}} {{term|varken||pig|lang=dum}}).<ref name=WID/><ref name=AHD>Morris, William, (1971)</ref> Early European colonists in South Africa noticed that the animal was similar to a pig, while "aarde" hints at the animal's habit of burrowing.

