===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The [[nocturnal]], [[insectivorous]], burrowing, [[mammal]] ''[[Orycteropus afer]]'', of the order ''[[Tubulidentata]]'', somewhat resembling a [[pig]], common in some parts of sub-Saharan Africa. {{defdate|from late 18<sup>th</sup> c.}}<ref name=SOED/>
#: ''The aardvark burrows in the ground and feeds mostly on termites, which it catches with its long, slimy tongue.
# {{slang|particularly in the southeast|_|US}} A [[silly]] or [[credulous]] person who is prone to [[mistakes]] or [[blunders]].
#: ''I walked into the wrong bathroom like a total '''aardvark'''.''

